articles.title: NK cell-mediated tumor cell killing by bispecific innate cell engagers induces ADCC-mediated activation of primary human dendritic cells.
articles.summary: Bispecific antibodies targeting NK cells can activate dendritic cells and enhance anti-tumor immune responses, potentially improving cancer treatment.
